posting_body: This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 641 Sq.
Be among the first to live in The Spring District in Bellevue, Washington.
We are creating a neighborhood that draws people in, sparks both business and personal passions weaving an intellectual tapestry that drives new ideas.

Not to mention innovative Townhomes and Live work lofts.
